data.description: Welcome to your next lucrative investment project! This charming ranch-style home in the heart of Tipp City presents a golden opportunity for savvy investors and DIY enthusiasts alike. With 1,014 square feet of potential waiting to be unlocked, this 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom gem is a blank canvas for your remodeling dreams. Nestled in the desirable Tipp City neighborhood, this property offers convenience and a strong sense of community. With a little TLC, this home has the potential to shine brightly. Imagine the possibilities and the return on investment! Situated on a generous lot, there's plenty of room for expansion or landscaping enhancements. A one-car detached garage provides secure parking and storage space for your projects and tools. The open layout of the living and dining areas offers flexibility for your design vision. Abundant windows throughout the home fill the space with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Whether you're an experienced investor or a first-time flipper, this property is ripe for transformation and profit potential. Benefit from the highly-rated Tipp City School District, making this property attractive to families. Don't miss out on this exceptional investment opportunity! With its prime location and potential for a stunning transformation, this property won't last long. Seize the chance to turn this house into a lucrative flip or your dream home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and start planning your renovation journey! Cash-only offers.
